videos.description: West Virginia guard Sean McNeil drives up to the 3-point line and drains the long range bucket with ease.

videos.description: Sean McNeil knocks down a 3-pointer to give the Mountaineers a 12-point lead.

videos.description: The West Virginia Mountaineers advance to 2-0 on the season as they take down the VCU Rams 78-66 behind Derek Culver's double-double of 23 points and 15 rebounds.
